trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> class contains information about a trust relationship between two <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> contém informações sobre uma relação de confiança entre dois objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the excluded top-level names in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os nomes de nível superior excluídos no objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" />.

trans-unit.source: A read/write <see cref="T:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection" /> that contains the excluded top-level names in the current object.
trans-unit.target: Uma leitura/gravação <see cref="T:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection" /> que contém os nomes de nível superior excluídos no objeto atual.

trans-unit.source: Commits any changes to the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> properties to the Active Directory Domain Services store.
trans-unit.target: Confirma as alterações realizadas nas propriedades <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> no repositório do Active Directory Domain Services.

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: Uma chamada ao serviço do diretório subjacente resultou em um erro.

trans-unit.source: A collision occurred with an existing trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Ocorreu uma colisão com uma relação de confiança existente.

trans-unit.source: Gets the top-level names in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os nomes de nível superior no objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" />.

trans-unit.source: A read-only <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollection" /> object that contains the top-level names in the current object.
trans-unit.target: Somente leitura <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollection" /> objeto que contém os nomes de nível superior no objeto atual.

trans-unit.source: Gets the trusted domain information for this <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém as informações de domínio confiável para este objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation" />.

trans-unit.source: A read-only <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInfoCollection" /> object that contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation" /> object for the current object.
trans-unit.target: Somente leitura <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInfoCollection" /> objeto que contém o <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation" /> objeto para o objeto atual.
